  "body": "[Beacon APIs v2.4.0](https://github.com/ethereum/beacon-APIs/releases/tag/v2.4.0) introduce a new node [example](https://github.com/ethereum/beacon-APIs/blob/master/apis/node/health.yaml) that do not pass currently on lodestar. \r\n\r\nAt first glance it looks related to a [limitation](https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/blob/unstable/packages/api/test/utils/checkAgainstSpec.ts#L68) of the testing framework with schema validation.\r\n\r\n```shell\r\n  1) getHealth\r\n       getHealth_request:\r\n     Error: Invalid request against spec schema\r\n\r\n/query/syncing_status - must be integer\r\n\r\n{\"query\":{\"syncing_status\":\"206\"}}\r\n\r\n{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"query\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"syncing_status\":{\"type\":\"integer\",\"minimum\":1,\"maximum\":599}},\"required\":[\"syncing_status\"]}},\"required\":[\"query\"]}\r\n```",
